  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;divination;\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;alchemist 1, bard 1, sorcerer/wizard 1, summoner 1, unchained Summoner 1;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, F (a magnetized nail or nugget of ore)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;60 feet<br>\n    <strong>Area</strong>&nbsp;cone-shaped emanation<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;concentration, up to 1 minute/level (D)<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;none;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;no<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You detect any metal objects or creatures within a 60-foot cone.</p><p>You can specify all metal objects or one or more specific types of metal (such as silver, cold iron, or a type of skymetal) when you cast this spell; in the case of the latter, you detect only objects or creatures made of the specified metal.</p>\n</div>\n",
